    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-02-05T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-02-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="222"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d222">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">White</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Sherman</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-02-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 5, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Hamburg consul reports examination commenced and all fresh fruit admitted, except
                    81 cases where claim is made scale insect was found. No trouble about dried
                    fruit.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">White.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
